    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  multiples sclerosis, according to McDonald's criteria

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  lack of French language proficiency

          -  severe cognitive impairment

          -  severe aphasia

          -  substance addiction

          -  psychiatric troubles (except for treated major depression)

          -  other severe neurologic or somatic disease

          -  pregnant or breast feeding patient
      </textblock>
